data.description: NEW PRICE & NEW ROOF!  Not only a new roof but a NEW HVAC system as well!  Located close to everything you will find this freshly painted inside and out home.  Large den area with vaulted ceiling and a cozy brick fireplace. Plenty of counter and cabinet space in the kitchen for all your home cooked meals. Three bedrooms plus 2 full baths, 2 car carport, laundry room and more.  Enjoy the back deck overlooking a large fenced in yard.  All this and more for only $200,000.00 so don't delay call a Realtor today!!!
